# **SUMMARY**

I started my career working on smaller automation tasks before moving on to building larger data systems, and over time I have grown into a data scientist who can design and deliver end-to-end machine learning solutions. My work centers on turning messy operational data into models that actually guide decisions, whether that is through time-series forecasting, resource planning, or scaling pipelines across cloud platforms like Azure and AWS. I think about the business side as much as the technical side, which means I actually look at company goals, the flow of operations, and the kind of insights leaders need before I design any solution. Data pipeline architecture, predictive modeling in production, forecasting methods, and cloud deployment are where I spend most of my time, with a strong focus on applying them to logistics efficiency and real business resource challenges..
